    {
      "text": "have.",
      "start": 574.97,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "And how important it is to bring or",
      "start": 575.63,
      "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
      "text": "take points.",
      "start": 578.53,
      "duration": 0.68
    },
    {
      "text": "It's something I say a lot as an",
      "start": 579.73,
      "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
      "text": "Interista.",
      "start": 582.89,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Sommers, if they don't shoot at him, he",
      "start": 584.27,
      "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
      "text": "doesn't take the points.",
      "start": 587.17,
      "duration": 0.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Even if I don't want to talk about",
      "start": 588.87,
      "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
      "text": "it tonight.",
      "start": 591.05,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "So, the start was a handicap.",
      "start": 594.03,
      "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
      "text": "But I feel like Fabregas, as well as",
      "start": 596.73,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": "Coma's team, still has to take that decisive",
      "start": 599.97,
      "duration": 5.58
    },
    {
      "text": "step of maturity.",
      "start": 605.55,
      "duration": 0.6
    },
    {
      "text": "Because the goal he scored today, he didn't",
      "start": 606.57,
      "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
      "text": "learn anything.",
      "start": 610.47,
      "duration": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "He didn't learn anything in facing Allegri.",
      "start": 612.65,
      "duration": 5.26
    },
    {
      "text": "He pushes forward, he passes the ball to",
      "start": 618.49,
      "duration": 7.6
    },
    {
      "text": "Leao with a long shot.",
      "start": 626.09,
      "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
      "text": "It's a goal.",
      "start": 629.43,
      "duration": 0.72
    },
    {
      "text": "It's a team that, in that moment, brought",
      "start": 632.43,
      "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
      "text": "the game to Milan.",
      "start": 635.33,
      "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
      "text": "We know how they play.",
      "start": 638.65,
      "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
      "text": "You can't take a goal like that.",
      "start": 641.05,
      "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
      "text": "You can't take it.",
      "start": 643.87,
      "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
      "text": "If we want to take that decisive step,",
      "start": 645.67,
      "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
      "text": "then, of course, Coma did a great game",
      "start": 650.47,
      "duration": 4.26
    },
    {
      "text": "today.",
      "start": 654.73,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Actually, on the 1-1, because we saw",
      "start": 655.95,
      "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
      "text": "it, Milan tried to win the game with",
      "start": 660.27,
      "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
      "text": "the weapons they had.",
      "start": 663.31,
      "duration": 0.64
    },
    {
      "text": "They tried it, and then, Duvicas'",
      "start": 664.51,
      "duration": 12.3
    },
    {
      "text": "header, I don't remember the situation, I think",
      "start": 676.81,
      "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
      "text": "it was in the first half.",
      "start": 679.75,
      "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
      "text": "He created a couple of situations.",
      "start": 682.91,
      "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
      "text": "He also created Milan, Leao's shot, but if",
      "start": 686.57,
      "duration": 5.6
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm not mistaken, it was out of play.",
      "start": 692.17,
      "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
      "text": "There's something to say.",
      "start": 696.87,
      "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
      "text": "Milan, in my opinion, found a great Jashari.",
      "start": 700.33,
      "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
      "text": "I really liked Jashari in the openings, Leao's",
      "start": 704.13,
      "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
      "text": "assist, I don't know how much Allegri might",
      "start": 707.17,
      "duration": 6.02
    },
    {
      "text": "like him, but he's certainly an interesting player.",
      "start": 713.19,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": "I don't know how to celebrate him, but",
      "start": 719.23,
      "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
      "text": "he's the player that you need for that",
      "start": 721.29,
      "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
      "text": "propulsion, or how he fills the space.",
      "start": 726.21,
      "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
      "text": "Rabiot, guys, if he's there or not, he's",
      "start": 729.73,
      "duration": 4.3
    },
    {
      "text": "the most important player for me, at least",
      "start": 734.03,
      "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
      "text": "in terms of movement.",
      "start": 736.57,
      "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
      "text": "I repeat, his absence, combined with a Mignane",
      "start": 738.51,
      "duration": 3.74
    },
    {
      "text": "who makes a mess, are seven points away",
      "start": 742.25,
      "duration": 9.24
    },
    {
      "text": "from Inter.",
      "start": 751.49,
      "duration": 0.62
    },
    {
      "text": "I feel that this gap exists, also because",
      "start": 752.23,
      "duration": 4.54
    },
    {
      "text": "of what we've seen.",
      "start": 756.77,
      "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
      "text": "Everyone likes to talk about the match against",
      "start": 759.43,
      "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
      "text": "Juventus and how it brought Inter home, but",
      "start": 763.19,
      "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
      "text": "there are 24 other games, and in the",
      "start": 766.11,
      "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
      "text": "other 24, I saw that these seven points",
      "start": 770.25,
      "duration": 4.06
    },
    {
      "text": "put Inter on the pitch.",
      "start": 774.31,
      "duration": 5.24
    },
    {
      "text": "But, as every Inter fan knows, before the",
      "start": 779.59,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "derby, until the derby, there's little to judge.",
      "start": 784.23,
      "duration": 5.88
    },
    {
      "text": "I think Inter will get there.",
      "start": 790.71,
      "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
      "text": "There's another game, I think it's against Parma,",
      "start": 795.15,
      "duration": 4.62
    },
    {
      "text": "Inter vs.",
      "start": 799.79,
      "duration": 0.7
    },
    {
      "text": "Lecce, so let's see how it goes.",
      "start": 800.49,
      "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
      "text": "We'll see.",
      "start": 805.33,
      "duration": 0.54
    },
    {
      "text": "That will be the decisive turning point to",
      "start": 806.21,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "draw some conclusions.",
      "start": 809.21,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "text": "Gentlemen, let me know what you think, leave",
      "start": 815.29,
      "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
      "text": "a comment, and subscribe to the channel.",
      "start": 817.41,
      "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
      "text": "A big hug from Nesquik.",
      "start": 819.39,
      "duration": 1.48
    }
